OL,4,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GEmma, who's 47, needs a CT scan
OL,6,     Gfollowing a bike crash with a
OL,7,     Gbus. Josh, who's 33, has severe
OL,8,     Gback pain. Pamela, who's 87, is
OL,9,     Gworried that she may have a blood
OL,10,     Gclot in her leg.
OL,11,G2305F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics attend a suspected
OL,13,     Gdomestic assault, and treat a
OL,14,     Gwoman with a dislocated shoulder
OL,15,     Gand a confused man who has
OL,16,     Gcollapsed in the street with his
OL,17,     Gdog.
